{"tid":476666,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國玻璃心】友誼賽再遇雪山獅子旗？ 德華人或舉超大國旗撐場","createTime":"2017-11-22T08:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T08:42:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8eaf9d4def60007d054d77930c93ce05956fbb","tid":476666,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171122/large/1511337018_582e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171122%2Flarge%2F1511337018_582e.jpg&h=a624b139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周六(18日)，中國足協U20選拔隊（國家青年隊）在德國法蘭克福球場參加西南地區聯賽的首場友誼賽中，觀眾席上有人展示西藏的「雪山獅子旗」，中方隊員隨即以退出賽場抗議。本周六，U20選拔隊將進行第二場友誼賽。據德國黑森州電視台於當地時間21日報道，有主隊FSV法蘭克福的球迷揚言將在比賽中懸掛「言論自由」的橫額和雪山獅子旗，另有法蘭克福的華人表示，正在組織華人球迷，到球場舉起國旗為中國隊打氣。<br />\n<br />\n黑森州電視台報道稱，據FSV法蘭克福總裁格爾納透露，該球會的粉絲已經申請了標語橫額，以表明德國的言論自由。他們還想掛一面「雪山獅子旗」。格爾納表示，只要表達合法，球會就不會干預。接受當地傳媒採訪時，這名總裁揚言「不會對民主的基本權利讓步一厘米」。在首場比賽中展示「雪山獅子旗」的組織發言人表示，不排除在以後的比賽中繼續掛旗。<br />\n<br />\n在法蘭克福工作的華人球迷陳先生表示，當地和德國其他地方的華人正準備周六到球場為中國隊打氣。如果德方不阻止掛「雪山獅子旗」的行為，他們將拿出更大的中國國旗遮擋住對方的旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n前日，中國外交部發言人陸慷就事件回應，指中方堅決反對任何國家、任何組織、任何個人以任何形式和理由為「藏獨」反華分裂活動提供支持。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171122/57489819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171122%2F57489819&d=iZ8SjhuwUcEPij6oaX2b4IM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=9bfeffe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171122%2F57489819&h=5f83e652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171122/57489819</a>"},{"pid":"903e8a855c7e03ca606243d73ee49ffbf1b9523a","tid":476666,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"咁愛支那, 就放棄德國居留權, 放棄德國藉<br />\n<br />\n返去支那國做支那人啦<br />\n<br />\n點解外國會有排華呢？ 就係呢班人自己做成既！"},{"pid":"74f53ba7136b31ade8b6c3261415611eb1fa43cb","tid":476666,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/50cent2_CayG0_300x200cropcenter.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F50cent2_CayG0_300x200cropcenter.png&h=bc2269e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d0affaaa6e045768b50af7e49ab82a340e26270","tid":476666,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在法蘭克福工作的華人球迷陳先生表示，當地和德國其他地方的華人正準備周六到球場為中國隊打氣。如果德方不阻止掛「雪山獅子旗」的行為，他們將拿出更大的中國國旗遮擋住對方的旗幟。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無論過左多少年，無論係地球任何一處<br />\n支那人都係賤畜, 無改變過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/01la1p102a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F01la1p102a.jpg&h=4e6f5011&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c7c2b6fd33b625af306f5b5b011d94394b813c9","tid":476666,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"圖旗法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b99127d28772fd04ece40e99a397fd8e652525","tid":476666,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"人地話比掛 唔係代表比你遮住人 on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309c0e97f4a4b6621eff1ddc658e2b6bfde5cb12","tid":476666,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"支持，中華民族偉大復興教訓下德國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6bebc317a9e989d84ba050be80124260c7b63a","tid":476666,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"班支蛆好可悲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一